                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Can you give the debug output as you receive it, so I can better diagnose? I'm really not sure what the issue is; it may be intended behaviour, it may not, but I need to see that output, as well as a better description of what you expect the behaviour to be.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-02-14T11:48:36.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-02-14T11:48:36.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/20187",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ceriak",
                        "name": "ceriak",
                        "displayName": "Jo\u00f3 \u00c1d\u00e1m",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Sorry for the delay. Here's the output:\n\n{code}\narray(1) {\n  [0] => string(15) \"views\/anything\/\"\n}\n\nCaught exception: script 'index\/index.phtml' not found in path (Test\/views\/scripts\/:views\/anything\/)\n\narray(2) {\n  [0] => string(19) \"Test\/views\/scripts\/\"\n  [1] => string(15) \"views\/anything\/\"\n}\n{code}",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ceriak",
                        "name": "ceriak",
                        "displayName": "Jo\u00f3 \u00c1d\u00e1m",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-03-23T13:03:25.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-03-23T13:03:25.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/21262",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "The behavior you present is the expected and designed behavior. Paths in Zend_View are done as a LIFO stack, and new paths added are placed at the top of the stack. If a script is not found in one path, the next path is searched.\n\nIf you want or need different behavior, please extend Zend_View to provide it.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-04-22T10:16:09.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-04-22T10:16:09.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/21394",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ceriak",
                        "name": "ceriak",
                        "displayName": "Jo\u00f3 \u00c1d\u00e1m",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "But the new path is not added but set (setScriptPath())! It should delete all the previously set paths, shouldn't it?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ceriak",
                        "name": "ceriak",
                        "displayName": "Jo\u00f3 \u00c1d\u00e1m",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-04-22T13:45:59.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-04-22T13:45:59.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/25996",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "The ViewRenderer calls addBasePath(), not setScriptPath().",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-11-10T10:58:04.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-11-10T10:58:04.000+0000"
                }
            ]
        }
